amendatorysection.para: The Sector Partnership Program Fund is created. The fund terminates on July 1, 2025, and the State Treasurer shall transfer any money in the fund on such date to the Workforce Development Program Cash Fund.

source.note: The Revisor of Statutes has pursuant to section 49-769 correlated LB264, section 134, with LB265, section 16, to reflect all amendments.
Changes made by LB264 became operative May 22, 2025. Changes made by LB265 became operative July 1, 2025.
